<plot>"Aninag" ("Light's Play") is a 15-minute narrative shot in 35mm film. Isabel, a blind girl who journeys in a dream world formed through the emotions she feels, shortly plays with her new mystical friends "Saya" (Happiness) and "Pag-asa" (Hope). But soon, she is succumbed by her negative thoughts of becoming alone. Her life becomes endangered. And the question is: "how would she overcome her fear, helplessness and depression in this struggling situation?"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041027</url></doc>
